{"tid":1172031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Google、WiFi 聯盟禁制後「藍牙」或成壓垮華為的最後一著？","createTime":"2019-05-26T06:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T09:58:12.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa24b584fdab781981ea956b99bdea24933679d","tid":1172031,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2839029/org/8ddd0137cd8a4ba28fc1364e61dc6466.jpg/IwNCgVOkxVNbxrxtrg2etceQ7SbPe0RbUd5Da1HeQ2s?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2839029%2Forg%2F8ddd0137cd8a4ba28fc1364e61dc6466.jpg%2FIwNCgVOkxVNbxrxtrg2etceQ7SbPe0RbUd5Da1HeQ2s%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=1620d73c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華為 Huawei 陸續面對不同的禁制，除了最早期的 Google 外，近日更有 SD Association 及 WiFi Alliance 宣布對 Huawei 作出禁制，可說是四面楚歌，但原來情況未算最壞，因為擁有藍牙技術的 Bluetooth SIG 尚未宣布任何行動。若有關方面出手，將會使 Huawei 手機進一步陷入困境。（文：黎生）<br />\n<br />\n自美國商務部將華為 Huawei 列入黑名單後，多間擁有不同專利權的組織便宣布對 Huawei 作出禁制。雖然 Huawei 稱已有「Plan B」 面對 Google、Qualcomm 及 ARM 的禁制，但近日繼 SD Association 後，WiFi Alliance 亦參與其中，使 Huawei 或面對新一代波的困境。<br />\n<br />\n據 WiFi Alliance 表示，為配合美國商務部的決定，將會禁止 Huawei 參與組織的活動，但不會撤鎖其會員資格。雖然 Huawei 依然可以使用 Wi-Fi 技術，但卻有機會失去參與制訂未來新標準的資格，使 Huawei 產品對於新標準的應用處於一個既被動亦落後的位置。<br />\n<br />\n繼  SD Association 及 WiFi Alliance 後，坊間還預計 Bluetooth SIG 亦可能會有同類舉動。總部位處美國華盛頓的 Bluetooth SIG 擁有藍牙技術的專利，加上每款藍牙產品均需要得到 Bluetooth SIG 同意才能生產，若 Bluetooth SIG 參與禁制 Huawei 的行動將會帶來極大影響。若 Huawei 產品缺少了藍牙功能，意味手機將難以有效地與無線耳機、智能手錶、無線喇叭等進行互動，加上這類功能沒有所謂「Plan B」，故將會大大影響用家的使用體驗。<br />\n事實上，Google 亦早已看到上述的可能性，故此近日亦將 Huawei 的 P30 Pro 及 Mate X 旗艦手機從 <a href=\"http://Android.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAndroid.com&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=fc6b4f54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Android.com</a> 的建議手機中移除；Google 此一舉動，一方面回應美國官方的命令，另一方面亦對 Huawei 未來推出的產品投以不信任的一票。"},{"pid":"36a194989ddf77c389be31262973e8a3b46eb293","tid":1172031,"uid":102701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"華為應該可以轉型做手機殼"},{"pid":"79200d30251810acd70c1a1513cfad9e8c9e5a7d","tid":1172031,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36a194989ddf77c389be31262973e8a3b46eb293","tid":1172031,"uid":102701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"華為應該可以轉型做手機殼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a18ac8e0555a8d85b487ace30db89eb6a42c092","tid":1172031,"uid":161945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79200d30251810acd70c1a1513cfad9e8c9e5a7d","tid":1172031,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36a194989ddf77c389be31262973e8a3b46eb293","tid":1172031,"uid":102701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"華為應該可以轉型做手機殼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:22:42.000Z","msg":"或者Mon 貼"},{"pid":"9952b3603cd9c4a3468c8e5eb7c3371b739cc060","tid":1172031,"uid":39486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:38:03.000Z","msg":"可以差吾多宣佈執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af24351bb6a91417b390d72a72315ea2c4a43fa4","tid":1172031,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a18ac8e0555a8d85b487ace30db89eb6a42c092","tid":1172031,"uid":161945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79200d30251810acd70c1a1513cfad9e8c9e5a7d","tid":1172031,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36a194989ddf77c389be31262973e8a3b46eb293","tid":1172031,"uid":102701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"華為應該可